title: University to host John C. Knox Writing Contest for high school students (Waynesburg University)
text: ( Source : Waynesburg University ) Waynesburg University will host the second annual John C. Knox Writing Contest Saturday, Nov. 7. It is free and open to high school students in grades 10 through 12 who attend public, private or home schools
